<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-15T17:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="220" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d220">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.O.6.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="smallcaps">Article 16, paragraph 1</hi></head>
                        <dateline>
                            <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                        </dateline>
                        <p>Delete the text: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                <p>“Excess war material of Allied origin shall be placed at the
                                    disposal of the Allied or Associated Power concerned …” and
                                    replace it by the following text: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                        <p>“War material of United Nations origin shall be put at
                                            the disposal of the United Nation concerned …”</p>
                                    </quote></p>
                            </quote></p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>